DOC.TEXT:
   Here is the 62-37 roll call by which the
Senate voted to confirm T. Timothy Ryan Jr. as director of the
Treasury Department's Office of Thrift Supervision.
   On this vote, a yes vote was a vote to confirm Ryan while a no
vote was a vote to reject the nomination.
   Voting yes were 17 Democrats and 45 Republicans.
   Voting no were 37 Democrats and no Republicans.
   xxx denotes senators not voting.
